The ECRB1 single vane, double shaft style rotary actuator is offered in 7 sizes (10-100mm). Rotation angles of up to 270&#xb0; is possible for the entire series. The ECRB series offers smooth, step-free operation and long life expectancies in rugged service applications. Optional auto switches are available.
